'''Blue Sky Boulevard''' was a road on [[Corellia/Legends|Corellia]]. It led from downtown [[Coronet City/Legends|Coronet City]] into the [[Blue Sector/Legends|Blue Sector]], and gave the sector its name. [[Card's Tapcaf]] was located on this road.

